snippet.title: Complete Rayman Playthrough (DOS)
snippet.description:
Complete playthrough of Rayman (1995), back before Ubi Soft milked the franchise to death. The playthrough lists all cages, most lives and magicians in the levels.

Recorded on DosBox, there are some cycle speedup issues, that is DosBox, not my recording.

Video split in two, first is getting power ups and second is the actual levels with the cages.
0:30 - The Dream Forest
15:45 - Moskito (boss)
19:15 - Band Land
33:25 - Blue Mountains
49:50 - Mr Stone (boss)

53:40 - Pink Plant Woods
1:01:10 - Anguish Lagoon
1:05:40 - The Swamps of Forgetfulness
1:12:30 - Moskito's Nest
1:22:20 - Bongo Hills
1:35:20 - Allegro Presto
1:47:40 - Gong Heights
1:52:00 - Mr Sax's Hullabaloo
1:58:05 - Mr Sax (boss)
2:01:35 - Twilight Gulch
2:04:50 - The Hard Rocks
2:24:00 - Mr Stone's Peaks
2:35:15 - Eraser Plains
2:50:30 - Space Mama 1 (boss)
2:53:55 - Pencil Pentathlon
3:07:30 - Space Mama's Crater
3:25:40 - Space Mama 2 (boss)
3:29:45 - Crystal Palace
3:36:30 - Eat at Joe's
3:47:20 - Mr Skop' Stalactites
3:49:50 - Mr Skop (boss)
3:52:50 - Mr Dark's Dare
